    "Rows without approval activity use the available IP Discharge KPI at 100%.",
    "Because the source has no Position column, the cleaner identifies the applied workstream by reconciling the source Performance Score against the three documented weight sets, then recalculates the score independently.",
    "Achievement and final scores are intentionally uncapped to match the source workbook."
